{"title": "How Do I Take a Singular Day Off in the Appointment Calendar?", "body": "This article will cover how to take a singular day off in the appointment calendar.\n\nWithin the appointment calendar, click on New Appointment as if you are booking an appointment but select 'Unavailable' instead.\nAfter this, set the Duration of the time or how long the day off will take, the Reason and Notes \n\nOnce you click SAVE you will be unbookable for that day.\n  How to Use the Wait-list"}